snippet.title: Raji: An Ancient Epic Enhanced Edition - Announce Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Raji: An Ancient Epic is an action-adventure game set in ancient India. A
young girl named Raji has been chosen by the gods to stand against the demonic invasion of the human realm. 

#Raji #NintendoSwitch

Experience the story of Raji in a free Enhanced Edition Update that includes new game modes and revamped gameplay features! Coming to Nintendo Switch later this year. https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/raji-an-ancient-epic-switch/

Visit Nintendo.com for all the latest! http://www.nintendo.com/
